title: The Tube (BBC 2012) - Season 1
description:
A look behind the scenes of the London underground as it undergoes the biggest overhaul in its history, focusing on key members of staff and some of the problems they face.

The first series produced by Blast! premiered on BBC 2 on 20 February 2012 at 21:00 and ran for six weeks with a total of six episodes produced for the BBC.
